&lt;p&gt;Patch applied.   Major thanks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The only change I made was to add a flag to the base HttpAuthSupplier to allow any subclass to specify whether they need the request caching or not.   That eliminates the &quot;instanceof DigestAuthSupplier&quot; in the conduit and also allows us to do the same if we implement NTLM auth later on as that will also need request caching.&lt;/p&gt;
